    {
      "@id": "http://localhost:3000/id/epd/http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%3A3000%2Fid%2Fepd%2FB-EPD%2520023.0221.003-01.00.00%2520CEM%2520IIIB%252042%252C5%2520N-LHSR%2520bulk%2520%25E2%2580%259CECOPlanet%25E2%2580%259D%2520EN_%2520signed/sections",
      "@type": "EpdSectionSet",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "number": "11.1",
          "title": "Indoor air",
          "content": "SUBSTANCES TO INDOOR AIR, SOIL\n\nAND WATER DURING THE USE\n\nSTAG E\n\nCement is not in direct contact with indoorair. It is the cement-based products (concrete, mortar…) that are potentially in contact\n\nwith indoor air."
        },
        {
          "number": "11.2",
          "title": "Soil and water",
          "content": "Cement is not in direct contact with indoorair. It is the cement-based products (concrete, mortar…) that are potentially in contact\n\nwith indoor air.\n\nCement is not in direct contact withsoil and water. It is the cement-based products (concrete, mortar…) that are potentially incontact\n\nwith soil and water."
        },
        {
          "number": "12",
          "title": "DEMONSTRATION OF VERIFICATION 3|26B-EPDCEM III/B42,5 N-LH/SRbulk“ECOPlanet”",
          "content": "Cement is not in direct contact withsoil and water. It is the cement-based products (concrete, mortar…) that are potentially incontact\n\nwith soil and water.\n\nEN 15804+A2serves as the core PCR\n\nIndependent verification of the environmental declaration and data according to standard EN ISO 14025:2010\n\nInternal☐ External☒\n\nThird party verifier:[Evert VermautJan Olieslagerslaan 35,1800 Vilvoorde, rsterckx@vincotte.be]"
        },
        {
          "number": "13",
          "title": "lca interpretation",
          "content": "EN 15804+A2serves as the core PCR\n\nIndependent verification of the environmental declaration and data according to standard EN ISO 14025:2010\n\nInternal☐ External☒\n\nThird party verifier:[Evert VermautJan Olieslagerslaan 35,1800 Vilvoorde, rsterckx@vincotte.be]\n\nNot provided."
        },
        {
          "number": "16",
          "title": "ADDITIONAL INFORMATION ON REVERSIBILITY",
          "content": "Not applicable for this EPD.\n\nREVERSIBILITY\n\nNot applicable for this EPD."
        }
      ]
