        "notes": "Columns B5, B6, and B7 appear to be blank/empty in all data rows for this additional impact categories table. The table presents six additional environmental impact indicators beyond the core EN 15804 impacts. Explanatory text for various impact categories is provided on page 2 (section 9.1)."
