          "title": "Indoor air",
          "content": "TVOCmeasured by Eurofins (report392-2017-00243305_A_EN_WR_IAC GOLD) in 2017:\n\nCombined\n\nReporting limitCalculation of\n\nStandard\n\nVersion uncertainty Result\n\nVOC (μg/m³) TVOC\n\n[RSD(%)]\n\nCEN/TS 16516 October 2013 5 Toluene eq. 22% Pass"
