          "content": "TVOCmeasured by Eurofins (report392-2017-00243305_A_EN_WR_IAC GOLD) in 2017:\n\nCombined\n\nReporting limitCalculation of\n\nStandard\n\nVersion uncertainty Result\n\nVOC (μg/m³) TVOC\n\n[RSD(%)]\n\nCEN/TS 16516 October 2013 5 Toluene eq. 22% Pass\n\nVERIFICATION\n\nEN 15804+A2serves as the core PCR\n\nIndependent verification of the environmental declaration and data according to standard EN ISO 14025:2010\n\nInternal☐ External☒\n\nThird party verifier:\n\nAgnesStehmann-Schuurmans and Bob Roijen\n\nSGS INTRON B.V.\n\nDr. Nolenslaan 126, 6136 GV Sittard\n\nThe Netherlands\n\nbob.roijen@sgs.com\n\n®"
