      "additionalInformation": [
        "ADDITIONAL INFORMATION ON RELEASE OF DANGEROUS SUBSTANCES TO INDOOR AIR, SOIL AND WATER DURING THE USE STAGE\n\nINDOOR AIR\nThis material is not classified as dangerous by the European legislation. There is no dangerous substance, according to CE n° 1272/2008. The product does not need to be stamped, according to the CE directives (67/548/ECC or 1999/45/EC). A test following the ISO 16000 has been realized. The emission class the most beneficial is retained for this B-EPD.\n\nSOIL AND WATER\nNot applicable as this product is not in contact with water and soil.",
        "DEMONSTRATION OF VERIFICATION\n\nEN 15804+A2 serves as the core PCR\n\nIndependent verification of the environmental declaration and data according to standard EN ISO 14025:2010\nInternal ☐ External☒\n\nThird party verifier: Evert Vermaut\nVinçotte\nJan Olieslagerslaan 35 B-1800 Vilvoorde\nevermaut@vincotte.be\nFebruary 2021",
