        "Owner of the EPD, Responsible for the data, LCA and information: Etex services, Kuiermansstraat 1, 1880 Kapelle-op-den-Bos, Belgium. Tel : +32 (0) 15 71 82 83; For more information you can contact Peggy Van De velde, peggy.vandevelde@etexgroup.com",
        "EPD program, Program operator, Publisher of this EPD: B-EPD, Federal Public Service of Health / DG Environment, Galileelaan 5/2, 1210 Brussels, Belgium. www.environmentalproductdeclarations.eu",
        "Contact programma operator: epd@environment.belgium.be",
        "Based on following PCR documents: EN 15804+A2:2019, NBN/DTD B 08-001 and its complement",
