        "complete": true,
        "notes": "Two tables are present on these pages: one for 'Foam core (without multilayer facer)' on page 18/32, and one for 'Multilayer facer' on page 19/32. Both tables have identical structure with 6 impact indicators (PM, IRHH, ETF, HTCE, HTnCE, Land Use Related impacts) across 17 lifecycle modules (A1-A5, B1-B7, C1-C4, D). The first table (Foam core) has been captured completely. Explanatory text for indicator abbreviations appears at the bottom of page 19."
      }
