        "notes": "Table shows 6 additional impact indicators beyond EN 15804 core indicators. Column headers are rotated vertically. Modules B1-B7 are all marked as MND (Module Not Declared). Footer contains abbreviation definitions: HTCE = HUMAN TOXICITY – CANCER EFFECTS; HTNCE = HUMAN TOXICITY – NON CANCER EFFECTS; ETF = ECOTOXICITY – FRESHWATER; PM = PARTICULATE MATTER; IRHH = IONIZING RADIATION – HUMAN HEALTH EFFECTS."
      }
